---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Community Postings
metaDescription: Community-serving White Plains information reviewed through WPCNA posting standards.
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
{% from "components/macros.njk" import postingCard %}

<section class="image-hero image-hero-posting">
  <img src="{{ site.postingHeroImage | withPrefix }}" alt="{{ site.postingHeroImageAlt }}" loading="eager">
  <h1 class="image-hero-label">Community Postings</h1>
</section>

<section class="section posting-listing-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="posting-listing-count">
      <span class="archive-count">{{ communityPostings.all.length }} postings</span>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid">
      {% for posting in communityPostings.all %}
        {{ postingCard(posting) }}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-alt" id="posting-guidelines">
  <div class="wrap posting-page">
    <section class="posting-intro" aria-labelledby="posting-resource-heading">
      <h2 id="posting-resource-heading">A curated community resource</h2>
      <p>This page is for local information that serves White Plains residents and neighborhoods.</p>
      <p>WPCNA reviews submissions before anything is posted. The goal is to share useful civic, neighborhood, and community updates &mdash; not classifieds, advertising, or personal listings.</p>
      <p>Submitting an item does not guarantee it will be posted. If it fits WPCNA&rsquo;s guidelines, it may be shared on the site, circulated through the council, or used to help residents stay informed.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="card-grid card-grid-2 posting-grid">
      <article class="resource-card">
        <p class="eyebrow">What&rsquo;s welcome</p>
        <h3>Community-serving information</h3>
        <ul class="plain-list">
          <li>Neighborhood events, school picnics, cleanups, and local meetings</li>
          <li>Civic or educational efforts, including awareness campaigns and newsletters</li>
          <li>City-related notices such as hydrant flushing, road work, or public-interest updates</li>
          <li>Local initiatives that help residents stay informed or get involved</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="resource-card">
        <p class="eyebrow">What we don&rsquo;t post</p>
        <h3>Not classifieds or advertising</h3>
        <ul class="plain-list">
          <li>Yard sales, personal listings, or private services</li>
          <li>Business advertising, promotions, or commercial offers</li>
          <li>Unreviewed announcements or anything that must appear immediately</li>
          <li>Items unrelated to White Plains residents or neighborhood life</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <section class="posting-include" aria-labelledby="posting-include-heading">
      <h2 id="posting-include-heading">What to include</h2>
      <p>Please include the basics residents will need: what you are sharing, who it is for, when it happens, where it takes place, and any link WPCNA should use if the item is posted.</p>
      <p>Keep your message brief and clear. If WPCNA needs more information, someone may follow up.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="sidebar-card posting-form-card" id="posting-form" aria-labelledby="posting-form-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Submission form</p>
      <h2 id="posting-form-heading">Send something for review</h2>
      <p>Use this form to send community information to WPCNA. Submissions are reviewed before posting.</p>
      <p class="form-note">Your email address is used for follow-up and will not be published unless you specifically ask WPCNA to include it.</p>

      <form class="contact-form posting-intake-form" action="{{ site.postingApiUrl }}" method="POST" data-posting-form data-posting-api="{{ site.postingApiUrl }}">
        <input type="hidden" name="pageSource" value="{{ site.baseUrl }}/posting/">
        <input type="text" name="_honey" class="form-honeypot" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" aria-hidden="true">

        {# Honeypot hidden from real users; catches automated submissions. #}
        <div class="form-honeypot" hidden aria-hidden="true">
          <input id="posting-website" name="website" type="text" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" aria-label="Website">
        </div>

        <fieldset class="form-section">
          <legend>What is this?</legend>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="posting-subject">Posting/Event Title</label>
            <input id="posting-subject" name="subject" type="text" maxlength="160" autocomplete="off" required>
            <p class="field-help">Use the public-facing title residents would see if this is posted.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="form-grid form-grid-2">
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="posting-category">Category</label>
              <select id="posting-category" name="category" required>
                <option value="">Select a category</option>
                <option value="Neighborhood Event">Neighborhood Event</option>
                <option value="Civic / Public Meeting">Civic / Public Meeting</option>
                <option value="Volunteer / Cleanup">Volunteer / Cleanup</option>
                <option value="Public Notice">Public Notice</option>
                <option value="School / Youth Activity">School / Youth Activity</option>
                <option value="Arts / Culture">Arts / Culture</option>
                <option value="Community Education">Community Education</option>
                <option value="Senior / Family Activity">Senior / Family Activity</option>
                <option value="Public Safety / Infrastructure">Public Safety / Infrastructure</option>
                <option value="Neighborhood Association News">Neighborhood Association News</option>
                <option value="Other">Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <span class="form-label">Posting Type</span>
              <div class="choice-grid choice-grid-compact">
                <label><input type="radio" name="postingType" value="Event" required> Event</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="postingType" value="Notice"> Notice</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="postingType" value="Meeting"> Meeting</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="postingType" value="Volunteer opportunity"> Volunteer opportunity</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="postingType" value="Newsletter/update"> Newsletter/update</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="postingType" value="Other"> Other</label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset class="form-section">
          <legend>When and where?</legend>

          <div class="form-grid form-grid-3">
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="posting-event-date">Event Date</label>
              <input id="posting-event-date" name="eventDate" type="date">
              <p class="field-help">Use if time-based.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="posting-event-time">Event Time</label>
              <input id="posting-event-time" name="eventTime" type="time">
              <p class="field-help">Use if time-based.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="posting-location">Location</label>
              <input id="posting-location" name="location" type="text" maxlength="180" autocomplete="street-address">
              <p class="field-help">Use if location-based.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset class="form-section">
          <legend>Who is this for?</legend>

          <div class="form-field">
            <span class="form-label">Intended Audience</span>
            <div class="checkbox-grid">
              <label><input type="checkbox" name="audience" value="Neighborhood residents"> Neighborhood residents</label>
              <label><input type="checkbox" name="audience" value="Families"> Families</label>
              <label><input type="checkbox" name="audience" value="Students"> Students</label>
              <label><input type="checkbox" name="audience" value="Older adults"> Older adults</label>
              <label><input type="checkbox" name="audience" value="Civic groups"> Civic groups</label>
              <label><input type="checkbox" name="audience" value="Citywide residents"> Citywide residents</label>
            </div>
            <p class="field-help">Choose any that apply.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <span class="form-label">White Plains Affiliation</span>
            <div class="choice-grid">
              <label><input type="radio" name="whitePlainsAffiliation" value="White Plains resident or neighborhood group" required> Resident or neighborhood group</label>
              <label><input type="radio" name="whitePlainsAffiliation" value="White Plains school, civic, or nonprofit group"> School, civic, or nonprofit group</label>
              <label><input type="radio" name="whitePlainsAffiliation" value="City or public agency"> City or public agency</label>
              <label><input type="radio" name="whitePlainsAffiliation" value="Other White Plains connection"> Other White Plains connection</label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset class="form-section">
          <legend>Who is submitting this?</legend>

          <div class="form-grid form-grid-2">
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="posting-name">Contact Name</label>
              <input id="posting-name" name="name" type="text" autocomplete="name" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="posting-email">Contact Email</label>
              <input id="posting-email" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" required>
              <p class="field-help">Used for follow-up. Not published unless requested.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field form-grid-span">
              <label for="posting-organization">Organization/Group Name</label>
              <input id="posting-organization" name="organization" type="text" maxlength="140" autocomplete="organization">
              <p class="field-help">Optional, but helpful for review.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset class="form-section">
          <legend>Review details</legend>

          <div class="form-grid form-grid-2">
            <div class="form-field">
              <span class="form-label">Fundraising</span>
              <div class="choice-grid choice-grid-inline">
                <label><input type="radio" name="fundraising" value="No" required> No</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="fundraising" value="Yes"> Yes</label>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-field">
              <span class="form-label">Links Included</span>
              <div class="choice-grid choice-grid-inline">
                <label><input type="radio" name="linksIncluded" value="No" required> No</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="linksIncluded" value="Yes"> Yes</label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="posting-message">Main Description <span class="char-hint" data-char-count>900 characters</span></label>
            <p class="field-help">What is happening, who is it for, when and where does it occur, and what should residents know?</p>
            <p class="field-help form-example">Example: Share the purpose, organizer, practical details, and any link WPCNA should review.</p>
            <textarea id="posting-message" name="message" rows="7" maxlength="900" required></textarea>
            <p class="field-help">If links are included, paste them here.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="form-field form-confirmation">
            <label>
              <input type="checkbox" name="guidelinesConfirmed" value="yes" required>
              I understand WPCNA reviews submissions before posting and does not post classifieds, advertising, or personal listings.
            </label>
          </div>
        </fieldset>

        <p class="form-status" data-posting-status hidden></p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block" type="submit" data-posting-submit>Send for review</button>
        <p class="form-note">Submitting an item does not guarantee posting.</p>
      </form>
    </section>
  </div>
</section>
